Trade/Device Name(s): Audit™ MicroCV™ Free T4 / Free T3 Linearity Set
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for Audit™ MicroCV™ Free T4 / Free T3 Linearity Set, a five-level calibration verification and quality control material for Free T4 and Free T3 endocrine analytes
Indications for Use Summary: For in vitro diagnostic use as a five-level linearity set and quality control material for Free T4 and Free T3 analytes in quantitative assays on automatic analyzers
